{"tid":491212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"free rider 點解可以咁黑人憎？","createTime":"2017-12-06T09:44:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T11:08:14.000Z","uid":161939,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"87847b59a8100c929c38fd9ae735e67f347e8912","tid":491212,"uid":161939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:44:25.000Z","msg":"唔知大家有無遇過一個free rider 係會 唔做嘢之餘仲會鬧一個有做嘢嘅組員呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交報告嘅前一日，佢就話不如我哋成組人一齊去食好西，咁我就黑面話佢，我哋真係好多嘢要做唔似你咩都唔洗做可以輕輕鬆鬆周圍玩，因為佢以為自己交咗俾我嘅報告就係交咗嘢（其實佢只係100%咁抄左人份source，就當交左貨俾我地），就要我同另一個組員仲要幫手做埋佢果部份。<br />\n<br />\n當我以爲交咗份報告就算啦無其他嘢煩，點知原來佢周圍同其他人講我，話我黑佢面，話我方丈，仲叫其他組員一齊杯葛我⋯⋯講呢到，其實我可以點做⋯⋯⋯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde0e811d4f50e16ecaecc9b42f8b2dcc121b8d8","tid":491212,"uid":13288,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:19:56.000Z","msg":"我依加一個人做緊四個人野 諗住交報告果陣唔寫佢地名"},{"pid":"de21c182d0b9274896f7d421cef3ea882e5a24a1","tid":491212,"uid":123456,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T10:24:41.000Z","msg":"標準做法：<br />\n1) report<br />\n2) 放佢上黎等其他人唔好再中伏"},{"pid":"dc2368357df8098b811ffb6b7c3933e634d08773","tid":491212,"uid":161939,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我依加一個人做緊四個人野 諗住交報告果陣唔寫佢地名</blockquote><br />\n我都唔想寫佢個名 但我啲組員衰心軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa1d4834240a9e3a7d2402e374ffa52dac3cfcaa","tid":491212,"uid":162023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"一早踢9佢出group<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75d6f13026f70daa8f5cf2bddffea1c72189408f","tid":491212,"uid":186159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201